    Contributing to the Website

    Bonjour my fellow HCREAMers. If you're reading this, then you have navigated to the blog section of the HCREAM website. I was always interested in creating a blog, so this will be my professional blog, along with yours as well.

    I propose that we use MkDocs to construct our website. If you look into the files, for example the one to create this page hcream.github.io/docs/blog/posts/creating-hcream-web.md, you can see that it is just a markdown file as is used in GitHub. There are a few extensions added, such as the template Material for MkDocs which gives a poopy internet connection good loading times, plus it looks slick. Most importantly for us mathematics, we may write some simple \(\LaTeX\).
